:HELP NAME='ANZFILEBAT'.Analyze File Attributes in Batch - Help
:P.
This option will submit an immediate batch job called ANZFILES which
will analyze all files in the specified library and populate ANZFILA
and ANZFILC. These files will then be used in subsequent HA Tools 2000
options to display or print the results.
:P.
:NT. This option must be run before HA Tools 2000 menu options to
Display File Analysis, Print Analyzed File Analysis or Interactive
File Analysis.:ENT.
:EHELP.
